September 4, 1958. No. 116,

October Term, 1958.

American Broadcasting-Paramount Theatres, Inc., v. United States. Albert C. Bickford for appellant. Oscar H. Davis, then Acting Solicitor General, for the United States.

Appeal from the United States District Court for the Southern District of New York. Dismissed per stipulation pursuant to Rule 60 of the Rules of this Court.
